The resulting object will be shallow merged, meaning that newer top level objects will be included in the final object without taking into account nested properties. The transformation must be in DRAFT or CHANGES_REQUESTED status to be updated.

bearer_token
path Parameters
id
required

Authorizations:
bearer_token
path Parameters
id
required
string

The ID of the curator application to get.

Responses

https://$API_URL/admin/applications/curator/{id}

Process a particular curator application by its ID.

Process a particular curator application by its ID. The requesting user must be an administrator. Pass accept query parameter with true or false to accept or deny the application. Accepting the application will update the role of the applicant to EXPERT.

Authorizations:
bearer_token
path Parameters
id
required
string

The ID of the curator application to get.

query Parameters
accept
required
boolean

Whether the application is accepted or denied.

Responses

https://$API_URL/admin/applications/curator/{id}/process
